<%- include('layout/header', { title, extraCss }) %>

<div class="container my-5" id="sdgs">
  <h1 class="display-4 text-center mb-5">Sustainable Development Goals</h1>

  <div class="sdg-section mb-4 text-center">
    <img src="/images/sdgs.png" alt="Sustainable Development Goals" class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm" />
  </div>

  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-lg-10">
      <ol class="list-group list-group-numbered lead shadow-sm sdg-list">
        <li class="list-group-item"><span class="fw-semibold">No Poverty:</span> Eradicate poverty in all forms everywhere.</li>
        <li class="list-group-item"><span class="fw-semibold">Zero Hunger:</span> End hunger and ensure food security through sustainable agriculture.</li>
        <li class="list-group-item"><span class="fw-semibold">Good Health:</span> Guarantee healthy lives and well-being for all ages.</li>
        <li class="list-group-item"><span class="fw-semibold">Quality Education:</span> Provide inclusive and equitable education for everyone.</li>
        <li class="list-group-item"><span class="fw-semibold">Gender Equality:</span> Achieve equality and empower all women and girls.</li>
        <li class="list-group-item"><span class="fw-semibold">Clean Water &amp; Sanitation:</span> Ensure safe water and sanitation access for all.</li>
        <li class="list-group-item"><span class="fw-semibold">Affordable &amp; Clean Energy:</span> Provide sustainable, modern, and reliable energy.</li>
        <li class="list-group-item"><span class="fw-semibold">Decent Work &amp; Growth:</span> Promote inclusive economic growth and decent jobs.</li>
        <li class="list-group-item"><span class="fw-semibold">Industry, Innovation &amp; Infrastructure:</span> Build resilient infrastructure and foster innovation.</li>
        <li class="list-group-item"><span class="fw-semibold">Reduced Inequalities:</span> Decrease inequality within and among countries.</li>
        <li class="list-group-item"><span class="fw-semibold">Sustainable Cities:</span> Make cities inclusive, safe, and environmentally friendly.</li>
        <li class="list-group-item"><span class="fw-semibold">Responsible Consumption:</span> Ensure sustainable production and consumption patterns.</li>
        <li class="list-group-item"><span class="fw-semibold">Climate Action:</span> Take urgent action to combat climate change.</li>
        <li class="list-group-item"><span class="fw-semibold">Life Below Water:</span> Conserve oceans and marine resources.</li>
        <li class="list-group-item"><span class="fw-semibold">Life on Land:</span> Protect forests, biodiversity, and ecosystems.</li>
        <li class="list-group-item"><span class="fw-semibold">Peace, Justice &amp; Institutions:</span> Promote peace, justice, and strong institutions.</li>
        <li class="list-group-item"><span class="fw-semibold">Partnerships for the Goals:</span> Strengthen global cooperation for sustainability.</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="videos mt-5 py-4 bg-light">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="h3 text-center mb-4">More Information About the 17 SDGs</h2>
    <div class="row g-4 justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="ratio ratio-16x9 rounded overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
          <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/o08ykAqLOxk" title="What are the SDGs?" allowfullscreen></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="ratio ratio-16x9 rounded overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
          <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/enGJyhu6Xr0" title="The 17 Goals Explained" allowfullscreen></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

